modName: DIMONIZED UNP clothing resources in a chest
summary: Pretty much what the title says.
descriptionHtml:
ADMINS IF THIS IS NOT SOMETHING I WAS ALLOWED TO UPLOAD OR DIMON WISHES REMOVED PLEASE CONTACT ME AND I WILL GLADLY REMOVE IT

This mod adds all of the clothing from dimon99\'s \"DIMONIZED UNP clothing resources\" to a chest inside the main area of QASMOKE. That\'s it, this is just an ESP file, you still need dimon\'s original work and all requirements that go along with it.

dimon\'s original mod can be found here: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/11882/?

flagged as \"adult\" because it links to the original work
All credit to dimon99
author: DarthFalcon
